  "detailed_description": "\"In Souls of Shadow, players will be immersed in a mysterious and ancient world filled with dark magic and endless adventure. Set in a land devoid of hope, an epic battle brews, and you will be the key to its outcome. As a destined hero set to alter the course of history, you embark on a challenging journey in pursuit of lost power and hidden truths.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/69b26be978dceb4e9f62b4473e9fcb00.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/69b26be978dceb4e9f62b4473e9fcb00.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/69b26be978dceb4e9f62b4473e9fcb00.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this perilous realm, you'll face a variety of enemies and monsters, requiring you to employ your skills and wit to overcome them. By exploring ancient ruins and dark dungeons, you'll unravel the secrets of this world and uncover the power concealed within the shadows. Meanwhile, your choices will determine the fate of the entire world, with each action having far-reaching consequences.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/dfb3e52b440ab85f296b96f405d6f44c.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/dfb3e52b440ab85f296b96f405d6f44c.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/dfb3e52b440ab85f296b96f405d6f44c.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Souls of Shadow seamlessly blends deep role-playing elements with thrilling action combat, delivering an unparalleled adventure for players. Get ready to embrace the challenge, uncover the truth, and save this world engulfed in darkness!\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/ae9a6cdcf2e3c2301e90315837ae8f9a.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/ae9a6cdcf2e3c2301e90315837ae8f9a.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/ae9a6cdcf2e3c2301e90315837ae8f9a.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/57bdda2eb18ff1826f2d1a82869d82e4.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/57bdda2eb18ff1826f2d1a82869d82e4.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/57bdda2eb18ff1826f2d1a82869d82e4.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/5ca18fb0a203c4eb64fc9aee2444bdb6.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/5ca18fb0a203c4eb64fc9aee2444bdb6.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/5ca18fb0a203c4eb64fc9aee2444bdb6.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"In Souls of Shadow, players will be immersed in a mysterious and ancient world filled with dark magic and endless adventure. Set in a land devoid of hope, an epic battle brews, and you will be the key to its outcome. As a destined hero set to alter the course of history, you embark on a challenging journey in pursuit of lost power and hidden truths.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/69b26be978dceb4e9f62b4473e9fcb00.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/69b26be978dceb4e9f62b4473e9fcb00.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/69b26be978dceb4e9f62b4473e9fcb00.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this perilous realm, you'll face a variety of enemies and monsters, requiring you to employ your skills and wit to overcome them. By exploring ancient ruins and dark dungeons, you'll unravel the secrets of this world and uncover the power concealed within the shadows. Meanwhile, your choices will determine the fate of the entire world, with each action having far-reaching consequences.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/dfb3e52b440ab85f296b96f405d6f44c.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/dfb3e52b440ab85f296b96f405d6f44c.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/dfb3e52b440ab85f296b96f405d6f44c.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Souls of Shadow seamlessly blends deep role-playing elements with thrilling action combat, delivering an unparalleled adventure for players. Get ready to embrace the challenge, uncover the truth, and save this world engulfed in darkness!\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/ae9a6cdcf2e3c2301e90315837ae8f9a.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/ae9a6cdcf2e3c2301e90315837ae8f9a.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/ae9a6cdcf2e3c2301e90315837ae8f9a.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/57bdda2eb18ff1826f2d1a82869d82e4.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/57bdda2eb18ff1826f2d1a82869d82e4.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/57bdda2eb18ff1826f2d1a82869d82e4.mp4?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/5ca18fb0a203c4eb64fc9aee2444bdb6.poster.avif?t=1719498094\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860670/extras/5ca18fb0a203c4eb64fc9aee2444bdb6.webm?t=1719498094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto